      "solution": "import sys\n\ndef next_palindrome_time(time_str):\n    hh, mm = map(int, time_str.split(':'))\n    while True:\n        mm += 1\n        if mm == 60:\n            mm = 0\n            hh = (hh + 1) % 24\n        s = f\"{hh:02d}{mm:02d}\"\n        if s == s[::-1]:\n            return f\"{hh:02d}:{mm:02d}\"\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    time_str = sys.stdin.readline().strip()\n    print(next_palindrome_time(time_str))\n",
